Class MemberDatabase

java.lang.Object
com.example.project3.MemberDatabase
public class MemberDatabase extends Object
The MemberDatabase class contains an array of all members in the fitness chain and various manipulations on the array.
Author:
Sneha Balaji, Ishita Bhargava
